  "2337310": {
    "name": "A Viking's Quest, the Lost Continent",
    "steam_appid": 2337310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/7c45954d633a3993cc08560518fbe0c9.poster.avif?t=1699712066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/7c45954d633a3993cc08560518fbe0c9.webm?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/7c45954d633a3993cc08560518fbe0c9.mp4?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>游戏内容是什么？</strong><br>受经典RPG和农场游戏的启发，《维京人的探险，失落的大陆》是一款引人入胜且充满活力的角色扮演游戏，您将体验一个精美手工打造的幻想与冒险世界。在这个游戏中，您将与这个失落大陆的生活、植物和生物互动，最终揭示您在这个幻想世界中的真正命运！<br><br>- 您可以从我们的网站了解更多关于游戏的信息:   或者来自我们的YouTube频道: <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/1f061ec3edf64a974146c7df22a34bd0.avif?t=1699712066\" width=600 height=450 /></span><br>'维京的探险'被设计为一款2D俯视角游戏，具备RPG和探索元素，同时也融入了一些生存特点。受到像 'Stardew Valley'、'Don't Starve' 等热门游戏的启发，它将包含一些生存机制和农业元素。然而，我们的游戏主要专注于探索和动作，具有合作游戏和进度。<br><br>此外，游戏还包括一个侧向滚动的海洋潜水游戏机制，让您可以探索这个失落的幻想大陆上精美手工制作的海洋生态区。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/69a388dd2239436f3dccd707d5375265.avif?t=1699712066\" width=680 height=1148 /></span><br><br><strong>角色定制</strong><br><br>在你的冒险中，你可以按照自己的意愿和喜好定制你的角色。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/733dcb5d23b740c76feafa7d35e2d26a.avif?t=1699712066\" width=600 height=318 /></span><br><br><strong>资源采集</strong><br>在这个失落的大陆上，资源采集包括从野生植物中采集、收集种子、耕种、狩猎、烹饪和开采矿石。当你以童心般的好奇心踏入《维京的探险》的世界时，你可以期待发现丰富多样的植物和动物生活，体验发现稀有植物、生物甚至宠物的兴奋。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/58e736d2895039c4506a4505116f66a8.poster.avif?t=1699712066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/58e736d2895039c4506a4505116f66a8.webm?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/58e736d2895039c4506a4505116f66a8.mp4?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/8f430423589f9f1317c51c8ed29e292c.poster.avif?t=1699712066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/8f430423589f9f1317c51c8ed29e292c.webm?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/8f430423589f9f1317c51c8ed29e292c.mp4?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>战斗</strong><br>在《维京探险》的世界里，战斗既刺激又有趣！近战和远程战斗都流畅而迅速。你可以跳跃或移动并同时攻击，这使得战斗更具冲击力和乐趣！你将有机会在战斗中遇到各种大小的生物。对于那些不太擅长战斗的人，你可以专注于幻想故事的一部分，遇见黑暗森林中的奇怪生物！谁知道，你也许会交上一位小精灵的朋友。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/7e08c6fa10870b91523f9f14349aabd0.poster.avif?t=1699712066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/7e08c6fa10870b91523f9f14349aabd0.webm?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/7e08c6fa10870b91523f9f14349aabd0.mp4?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>多人游戏玩法</strong><br>你可以在线或局域网上享受《维京的探险》中有趣的合作游戏，与朋友一起探索失落的大陆，度过愉快时光！<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/2dd30e130fffa45b264f74b95674d52e.poster.avif?t=1699712066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/2dd30e130fffa45b264f74b95674d52e.webm?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/2dd30e130fffa45b264f74b95674d52e.mp4?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>天气系统</strong><br>天气系统旨在与游戏机制协同工作。有昼夜循环控制着天气以及它如何影响大陆上的生物。失落的大陆上有不同的气候适用于不同的地区。这些地区包括：(1) 雨林和沼泽地，(2) 高地，(3) 山区，(4) 沙漠，以及 (5) 冰雪覆盖的山脉。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/d47ae4c6110ce30dd7732adaf6f66a9a.poster.avif?t=1699712066\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/d47ae4c6110ce30dd7732adaf6f66a9a.webm?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2337310/extras/d47ae4c6110ce30dd7732adaf6f66a9a.mp4?t=1699712066\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
